Requirements
------------
Game:
    Qt >= 5.0 (system or SDK)

Editor:
    Qt >= 5.0 (system or SDK)

Documentation:
    doxygen
    graphviz

Compiling
---------

Game:

$ cd game/src
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ <see below>
$ make
$ cd ../..
$ ./gtg

Step 4: If you are using system's Qt5, run

$ cmake ..

otherwise, if you are using Qt's SDK, run

$ cmake .. -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=/<QTSDK-PATH>/<VERSION>/<YOUR-COMPILER>/cmake


Editor:

$ cd editor
$ qmake
$ make
$ ./editor

If you are using Qt's SDK, run this first:

$ export PATH="$PATH:/<QTSDK-PATH>/<VERSION>/<YOUR-COMPILER>/bin"

Documentation:

$ cd game
$ doxygen Doxyfile
$ <your-browser> doc/html/index.html
